  "body": "As per this line https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/master/packages/hardhat-solhint/src/index.ts#L88 the .solhintignore file is never read. `npx hardhat check` will run solhint using all files in the `config.paths.sources`.\r\n\r\nReproduce:\r\n\r\n```\r\n## .solhintignore\r\nMyContract.sol\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\nnpx hardhat check\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n// output showing errors for MyContract.sol\r\n```\r\n",
